text.__SUMMARY__: The Cayman Brac blind snake (Cubatyphlops epactius) is a species of snake in the family Typhlopidae.
text.Geographic range: C. epactius is endemic to the Cayman Islands.
text.Habitat: The preferred habitats of C. epactius are coastal marine, supratidal, and forest at altitudes of 2–5 m (6.6–16.4 ft).
